name: Unstoppable Train!
text:
You don't have to Tribute monsters when you Normal Summon/Set a monster during this turn.
The effects of monsters you Normal Summon/Set during this turn will be negated.
This Skill can only be used if you begin the Duel with a Deck (excluding Extra Deck) that follows the conditions below. This Skill can only be used twice per Duel.
● Your Deck contains 10 or more monsters.
● All monsters in your Deck are Level 4 or 10 monsters.
● All monsters in your Deck are EARTH Machine-Type monsters with 1800 or higher ATK.
